程序包 <Unnamed>

  • 类概要 
    类 说明
    Attribute
    Represents an attribute in a card.
    Card
    The Card class represents cards, contains memebers card names and attributes, and provides methods about card itself and attributes.
    DataInput
    The InputOutput class implements several method taking the human input from the keyboard.
    Game
    The Game class implements the interactive game procedure by quite a few global attributes and methods.
    Human
    The Human class inherits from the Player class, and implements the abstract method selectAttribute().
    Main
    The Main class is to instantiate the game.
    Player
    The abstract Player class represents general players, contains memebers of player names and cards, provides methods about card itself and attributes, and is inherited by other subclasses.
    PredictableComp
    The PredicatbleComp class inherits from the Player class, and implements the abstract method selectAttribute().
    RandomComp
    The RandomComp class inherits from the Player class, and implements the abstract method selectAttribute().
    SmartComp
    The SmartComp class inherits from the Player class, and implements the abstract method selectAttribute().
